OL,5,Ckiller
OL,7,FAnnouncing the Care Quality Commission
OL,8,F(CQC) review, Health Secretary
OL,9,FVictoria Atkins said: "My thoughts
OL,10,Fremain with the families and friends
OL,11,Fof Barnaby, Grace and Ian, who lost
OL,12,Ftheir lives in such a tragic, cruel
OL,13,Fand barbaric way.
OL,15,F"It is crucial that our mental health
OL,16,Fservices ensure both the care of
OL,17,Fpatients and the safety of the public.
