OL,7,FThe Government has asked the regulator
OL,8,Fto assess the progress made by the
OL,9,Fhospital to improve standards since
OL,10,Fthat inspection.
OL,12,FDirector of mental health at the CQC,
OL,13,FChris Dzikiti said: "We will conduct a
OL,14,Frapid review into mental health
OL,15,Fservices in Nottingham to understand
OL,16,Fwhether there are any practical
OL,17,Factions which can be taken to improve
OL,18,Fthe quality of services and ensure
OL,19,Fpeople receive safe and effective care.
