OL,7,FIn a statement Ifti Majid said: "We
OL,8,Fwelcome external inspections as they
OL,9,Fare important to helping us learn and
OL,10,Fcontinually improve our services,
OL,11,Fgiving us independent insight to
OL,12,Fhighlight areas for development so
OL,13,Fthat the experience for those who use
OL,14,Four services is improved.
OL,16,F"We look forward to working with the
OL,17,FCare Quality Commission and NHS
OL,18,FEngland, and we undertake to swiftly
OL,19,Fimplement any recommendations.
